\par }\pard\plain \qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid7603589 \f56\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\cgrid\langnp2057\langfenp2057 {\insrsid7603589 
\par Numerous alternatives have been proposed. These tend to be along the lines of those outlined earlier in this section. They range from the following:
