\jclisttab\tx360\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\ls38\adjustright\rin0\lin360\itap0\pararsid8723256 {\f56\fs22\insrsid7603589\charrsid6428464 Key access issues for the South, such as \lquote indigenous (or traditional) knowledge\rquote 
